{"title": "Your Genesis Artwork", "slug": "your-genesis-artwork", "date": "2021-08-17", "author": "theline1", "excerpt": "", "categories": ["Alistair Keddie", "Idil Mohamed", "Keegan Westervelt", "News On The Line"], "featuredImage": "https://theline.wtf/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/QmWtHn3HBUKnq4LPT4g1DiX49AvkWmQJWcTXEznQBMpVQi.jpeg", "images": ["https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2021/08/E82xMTFVgAA8S5l.jpeg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2021/08/nft-11.jpg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/E82xMTFVgAA8S5l.jpeg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/nft-11.jpg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-17-at-4.07.23-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-17-at-3.36.38-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/E82xMTFVgAA8S5l.jpeg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/nft-12.jpg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2021/08/nft-11.jpg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2021/08/nft-12.jpg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2021/08/nft-12.jpg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/QmdrXKidZSQaApGWJNnimL6qVKeN6Q9aHuXYpuigk57xy9.jpeg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-17-at-4.20.05-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/nft-10.jpg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-17-at-3.36.38-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/09/unnamed-24.jpg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-17-at-4.20.05-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2021/08/E82xMTFVgAA8S5l.jpeg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/nft-8.jpg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-17-at-4.07.23-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/QmdrXKidZSQaApGWJNnimL6qVKeN6Q9aHuXYpuigk57xy9.jpeg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/nft-12.jpg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/nft-11.jpg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-17-at-3.36.38-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-17-at-4.07.23-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/nft-8.jpg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/nft-10.jpg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-17-at-3.36.38-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2021/08/nft-8.jpg", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w2400/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-17-at-3.36.38-PM.png", "https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2021/08/QmdrXKidZSQaApGWJNnimL6qVKeN6Q9aHuXYpuigk57xy9.jpeg"], "content": "<p>Your genesis artwork is the very first artwork or series you mint. It's the first time you decided to share your creativity on the blockchain for collectors to buy. Fortunately, there are collectors searching for genesis works too.  </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">One of my fav thing to do is find a new Artist and give them that first sale.<br /><br />I remember making my first $2.80 on the internet 12 years ago.<br /><br />It was the sweetest, one of the most happiest moments of my life.</p>&mdash; Matty (@DCLBlogger) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/DCLBlogger/status/1427223101834547201?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 16, 2021</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><p>Today's MintFace explores genesis art by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/alistairkeddie\">Alistair Keddie</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/idillmohamed\">Idil Mohamed</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/goku_nft\">Keegan Westervelt</a>.</p><h2 id=\"mintface-artist-featurealistair-keddie\"><strong>MintFace Artist Feature - Alistair Keddie</strong></h2><p><em>Photographer &amp; visual artist drawing on landscape, being &amp; place using photography, photomontage &amp; abstract paint.</em></p><p>Beinn Achaladair is a Scottish mountain that rises up at a modest 1,038 elevation. <a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/0x495f947276749ce646f68ac8c248420045cb7b5e/72505513136777446701419000360783480055369670844013667197492043566175647432705\">Snow Field, Beinn Achaladair</a> is also the genesis art series that Alistair Keddie has selected for his first showing on the OpenSea marketplace.</p><blockquote>\"Strong sun lights a stretch of snow and craggy mountain from high up on Beinn Achaladair with views across Rannoch Moor and close to Bridge of Orchy - 3:18pm Saturday 4th March 2006.\" Alastair Keddie.</blockquote><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/E82xMTFVgAA8S5l.jpeg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1638\" height=\"2048\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/E82xMTFVgAA8S5l.jpeg 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2021/08/E82xMTFVgAA8S5l.jpeg 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2021/08/E82xMTFVgAA8S5l.jpeg 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/E82xMTFVgAA8S5l.jpeg 1638w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>Alba Dubh is the name of Alastairs genesis series of black and white photographs. Alba Dubh translates roughly as dark or black Scotland in the native Gaelic and these photographs emphasise the failing of light as they recede into distance and time according to Alistair. There are <a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/alba-dubh-dark-scotland\">eleven photographs in this series</a>. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Just dropped Alba Dubh, a deeply personal series of dark landscapes from home reflecting on memory and the passage of time. <br /><br />A share most appreciated <br /><br />First 11 on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/opensea?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@opensea</a> - all 1/1 @ 0.2Ξ<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/AlbaDubh?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#AlbaDubh</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/nftphotography?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#nftphotography</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/NFTcollection?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#NFTcollection</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/nftcollector?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#nftcollector</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/99oxJUu7N9\">https://t.co/99oxJUu7N9</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/m5b6WU8M0I\">pic.twitter.com/m5b6WU8M0I</a></p>&mdash; Al Keddie (@alistairkeddie) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/alistairkeddie/status/1426655738470932482?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 14, 2021</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><p>The Alba Dubh is his latest series though, not his genesis NFT ie: the first that was minted on the blockchain. That honour goes to <a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/0x495f947276749ce646f68ac8c248420045cb7b5e/72505513136777446701419000360783480055369670844013667197492043521095670693889\">'Ahead full of screens, a siren calls'</a></p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/09/unnamed-24.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"600\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/09/unnamed-24.jpg 600w\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/0x495f947276749ce646f68ac8c248420045cb7b5e/72505513136777446701419000360783480055369670844013667197492043521095670693889\">'Ahead full of screens, a siren calls'</a> by Alistair Keddie. Long exposure, black and white street photography from a series of Sun Glints, shot while walking Auckland, New Zealand. Edition: 1 of 1</figcaption></figure><p>Alistair's first NFT is part of the <a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/ghost-shimmer\">Ghost Shimmers collection</a> on the OpenSea marketplace. </p><blockquote>\"The Ghost Shimmers collection is a long exposure, black and white street photography from a series of Sun Glints, shot while walking in Auckland, New Zealand.\" Alistair Keddie.</blockquote><p>Does genesis mean new artist? Not necessarily. It definately means the first NFT minted by an artist. Alistairs provenance heralds from his studies at the Glasglow School of Art in the early 1980's, his portfolio of work is recognised by <a href=\"https://www.saatchiart.com/alistairkeddie\">Saatchi's Art</a>. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-17-at-3.36.38-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"568\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-17-at-3.36.38-PM.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-17-at-3.36.38-PM.png 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-17-at-3.36.38-PM.png 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w2400/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-17-at-3.36.38-PM.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/alba-dubh-dark-scotland\">Alba Dubh - Alistair Keddie's genesis series</a></figcaption></figure><p>Now living in Aotearoa, New Zealand... on the opposite side of the world from the subject matter featured in his OpenSea genesis series, Alistair's work has also evolved.</p><p>\"Something epic landscape, incandescent bright\" is <a href=\"https://foundation.app/@creator/nft-48610\">his genesis artwork on Foundation</a> minted 65 days ago according to <a href=\"https://etherscan.io/token/0x3B3ee1931Dc30C1957379FAc9aba94D1C48a5405?a=48610\">Etherscan records</a>.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/nft-8.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1344\" height=\"1680\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/nft-8.jpg 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2021/08/nft-8.jpg 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/nft-8.jpg 1344w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://foundation.app/@creator/nft-48610\">Something epic landscape, incandescent bright</a> - Alistair Keddie on <a href=\"https://foundation.app/@creator/nft-48610\">Foundation marketplace</a></figcaption></figure><p>Keep digging and you'll find Alistairs most affordable photographic on the <a href=\"https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/objkt/205125\">Hic et Nunc (HEN) marketplace</a> starting at just 1 Tez. My favourite? <a href=\"https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/objkt/205125\">No s\nafe distance</a>. The heavy editing in post turns an innocuous side of the Auckland highway into something more foreboding... with a foreground of vehicle artifacts breaking visual  expectations. While not a genesis work, it's cool nonetheless to see some of my home country minted on the blockchain.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/QmdrXKidZSQaApGWJNnimL6qVKeN6Q9aHuXYpuigk57xy9.jpeg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/QmdrXKidZSQaApGWJNnimL6qVKeN6Q9aHuXYpuigk57xy9.jpeg 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2021/08/QmdrXKidZSQaApGWJNnimL6qVKeN6Q9aHuXYpuigk57xy9.jpeg 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/QmdrXKidZSQaApGWJNnimL6qVKeN6Q9aHuXYpuigk57xy9.jpeg 1024w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/objkt/205125\">No Safe Distance</a> on <a href=\"https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/objkt/205125\">HEC marketplace</a> by Alistair Keddie</figcaption></figure><p>If you're an OpenSea ethereum genesis collection collector, start with <a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/ghost-shimmer\">Ghost Shimmer</a>.</p><h2 id=\"mintface-artwork-featureidil-mohamed\"><strong>MintFace Artwork Feature - Idil Mohamed</strong></h2><p>Idil Mohamed is a photographer based in Toronto so it makes sense for her genesis artwork to feature the iconic CN Tower. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/nft-10.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"972\" height=\"1680\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/nft-10.jpg 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/nft-10.jpg 972w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://foundation.app/@idil/city-walks-36100\">City Walks</a> by Idill Mohamed on <a href=\"https://foundation.app/@idil/city-walks-36100\">Foundation marketplace</a></figcaption></figure><blockquote>\"This photo was taken in Toronto’s Financial District and is by far one of my favourite photos. I remember standing in this exact spot waiting for someone to walk by for about an hour to capture the shot I had envisioned. I’m really happy that I waited because the photo came out to be everything I imagined and more.\"</blockquote><p>Selecting your genesis photo is also a promise to collectors of what's to come. If this is what we can expect next, then I'm more than excited to follow Idil's photographic journey on the Foundation marketplace. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">My genesis piece “City Walks” is still available on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/withFND?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@withFND</a>, this is by far one of my all-time favourite street/cityscape shots in one. <a href=\"https://t.co/lSwrC5R1HL\">https://t.co/lSwrC5R1HL</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/AVNezTBRi3\">pic.twitter.com/AVNezTBRi3</a></p>&mdash; idil (@idillmohamed) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/idillmohamed/status/1426575894412410887?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 14, 2021</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><p>The photograph was <a href=\"https://etherscan.io/tx/0xffce3c037a38bdd9b96b8ba27ed3b9ea6ed1892a4f00c0511d2f610fdfdac2d5\">minted on the blockchain on May 13th at 11:55pm</a> for those of you who care about timestamp provenance. </p><p>Idil offers a series of more recent perspectives of the <a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/toronto-a-city-of-colour?ltclid=174eefcf-c4db-4857-9e30-d5f578dd61e4\">CN Tower on the OpenSea marketplace</a>. There are ten to the collection named '<a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/toronto-a-city-of-colour?ltclid=174eefcf-c4db-4857-9e30-d5f578dd61e4\">Toronto: A City of Colour</a>' highlighting Toronto’s iconic landmark, the CN Tower.</p><blockquote>\"Ever since picking up a camera in 2018, I was inspired to capture the places that make up the vibrant city of Toronto. These photos were taken over the course of 4 years and represent my growth along my journey as a cityscape photographer. Each image features the CN Tower in different conditions and at varying distances, all of which showcase the beautiful colours that paint the city.\" Idil Mohamed.</blockquote><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-17-at-4.07.23-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1572\" height=\"748\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-17-at-4.07.23-PM.png 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-17-at-4.07.23-PM.png 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-17-at-4.07.23-PM.png 1572w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption>Idil's photography currently available for purchase on the <a href=\"https://opensea.io/collection/toronto-a-city-of-colour?ltclid=174eefcf-c4db-4857-9e30-d5f578dd61e4&amp;search[sortBy]=PRICE&amp;search[sortAscending]=true&amp;search[toggles][0]=BUY_NOW\">OpenSea marketplace</a></figcaption></figure><p>As I write this, I'm elated to see these photos...being half Canadian myself. How the cityscape has changed the skyline since I last visited in 1991! How good is <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CQ9HUi-DtOK/\">this photo</a>! (on Instagram so not available to purchase)</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Today’s sunrise in Toronto 🧡 <a href=\"https://t.co/E9VJXkc1UB\">pic.twitter.com/E9VJXkc1UB</a></p>&mdash; idil (@idillmohamed) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/idillmohamed/status/1412401647796563969?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">July 6, 2021</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><h2 id=\"mintface-sale-featurekeegan-westervelt\"><strong>MintFace Sale Feature - Keegan Westervelt</strong></h2><p><em>Discord lord. community manager. art admirer. crypto enthusiast. explorer of mediums.</em></p><p>'<a href=\"https://foundation.app/@goku_nft/calm-in-chaos-66030\">Calm in Chaos</a>' was the first artwork sale by Keegan Westervelt also known as <a href=\"https://twitter.com/goku_nft\">@Goku_NFT</a> on Twitter. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/nft-11.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1680\" height=\"1322\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/nft-11.jpg 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2021/08/nft-11.jpg 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2021/08/nft-11.jpg 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/nft-11.jpg 1680w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><blockquote>\"I still remember those first few months living in New York like they were yesterday, there was no better fast track way to getting a feel for the city than working in Times Square at random hours of the night.\"</blockquote><blockquote>\"There's a feeling that suddenly switches on once the Broadway shows have all closed and the tourist returned home.\"</blockquote><blockquote>\"In these hours moments of magic happen on the regular, often unseen or disregarded but to the few who pay attention.\"</blockquote><p>The photograph sold for 0.22 eth on August 4th 2021 from a single bid. Congratulations Keegan!</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-17-at-4.20.05-PM.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1360\" height=\"1278\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-17-at-4.20.05-PM.png 600w, https://digital-artist\n-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-17-at-4.20.05-PM.png 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/Screen-Shot-2021-08-17-at-4.20.05-PM.png 1360w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>If you missed this genesis sale, Keegan has listed his second '<a href=\"https://foundation.app/@goku_nft/the-woman-68949\">The Woman</a>' on the <a href=\"https://foundation.app/@goku_nft/the-woman-68949\">Foundation marketplace</a>.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/nft-12.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1680\" height=\"1265\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w600/2021/08/nft-12.jpg 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1000/2021/08/nft-12.jpg 1000w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/size/w1600/2021/08/nft-12.jpg 1600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2021/08/nft-12.jpg 1680w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><a href=\"https://foundation.app/@goku_nft/the-woman-68949\">The Woman by Keegan Westervelt</a> on <a href=\"https://foundation.app/@goku_nft/the-woman-68949\">Foundation marketplace</a></figcaption></figure><p>Today's MintFace shows that selecting your genesis artwork or series sets the stage for what your collectors will expect you to mint next. It also provides hope for those artists yet to sell their genesis artwork as there collectors who enjoy taking an early bet on early career artists or established artists new to digital artworks.</p><p>Whatever you decide, always listen to Keegan!</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Do whatever you believe in.</p>&mdash; Keegan (@goku_nft) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/goku_nft/status/1427443753426591747?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">August 17, 2021</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><hr /><p><em>Enjoying MintFace? Help keep it free by supporting the platform in one of two ways.</em></p><p><strong>Art Collectors</strong> - you can become a member to receive a secret weekly MintFace  surfacing artwork that others have missed. No apes. No punks. Just quality art by quality artists.</p><p><strong>Artists</strong> - you can send any notes of appreciation to <em><strong>ryanj.eth</strong></em> in whatever form you feel reflects your art.</p><p>If this article has made you curious about getting started with digital art, we also run the Digital Artist Economy workshop helping artists create their first digital art through a <a href=\"https://maven.com/cache/nft-digital-artist-economy\">three week programme.</a> Share it with an artist you'd like to see on an NFT marketplace.</p><p><strong>MintFace surfaces great artists and artworks so you don't have to. </strong></p><p></p>"}